data.joke: Why did the duck go to the doctor? Because it was feeling a little 'fowl'!
What do you get when you cross a duck with fireworks? Firequackers!
What did the duck say when it won the lottery? 'Waddle I do with all this money?'
Why did the duck refuse to fly south for the winter? Because it couldn't find a 'quacking' good reason!
How do ducks communicate during basketball games? They 'quack' the code!
What did one duck say to the other when they bumped into each other? 'Sorry, I didn't mean to 'quack' into you!'
Why did the duck go to space? To quack the mysteries of the universe!
What's a duck's favorite game? Duck Duck Goose, of course!
Why don't ducks ever get lost? Because they always know their 'quack' position!
How did the duck make friends? It was very 'down' to earth!
What do you call a duck that's a magician? A 'quack' conjurer!
Why did the duck bring a rose to the party? Because it wanted to 'quack' the ice!
What do you call a duck that loves to dance? A quackstep!
Why was the duck put into the army? Because it was an expert at 'duck and cover'!
What do you call a duck that's addicted to drugs? A 'quack' head!
Why did the duck become a comedian? Because its jokes always 'quack' everyone up!
What's a duck's favorite food? Quackers and cheese!
Why did the duck become a detective? To quack the case!
What did the duck say to the comedian? 'You quack me up!'
How do you know if a duck is in your refrigerator? You can hear the 'quack'!
